 Popular comedian Woli Arole has shared some good news as he announced to his fans and followers on Instagram that he would be getting married soon. The comic star is set to walk the aisle with the woman after his heart. Sharing the announcement in a beautiful way, Arole posted a set of pre-wedding pictures on his page. In one of the captions that accompanied the post, the comedian gushed over his woman while noting that she brought colour into his life Sharing another pre-wedding picture, Arole disclosed that their love journey started all the way in London. “A JOURNEY that started somewhere in LONDON.So glad I am walking down the AISLE with YOU. You’re a blessing to ME. Yemmy Yemmy like I love to call YOU. Ololufemi Owon,” he wrote.